Normal Map Nodegroups:

NormalMap_Combine-PD: ................combines normal maps partial derivatives.
NormalMap_Combine-Orientation: .......combines normal maps by reorienting detail onto base
NormalMap_Combine-Rotation: ..........combines normal maps by rotating detail onto base
NormalMap_Blend-PD: ..................blends two normal maps together by Combine-PD
NormalMap_Blend-Orientation: .........blends two normal maps together by Combine-Orientation
NormalMap_Scale: .....................scales a normal map
